      "message": "[error] Line 100: Adding `pluginData` to the positional DBus struct serialization changes the wire format. Any peer (daemon, client) that hasn\u0027t been rebuilt simultaneously will fail to deserialize `SwarmMessage` because the argument count no longer matches. This is a silent, hard-to-debug breakage. The DBus interface version or signature should be bumped to force detection of the mismatch.",
