      "message": "[warning] Line 128: `bodyOverwriteIt.value()` is copied from untrusted plugin data and stored directly as `body` with no length limit or content validation. If any downstream consumer renders this string as rich text or in a context that interprets markup, it is an injection vector. Apply the same sanitisation used for normal message bodies.",
