      "side": 1,
      "message": "[warning] Line 138: The key `bodyOverwrite_e%1` uses the loop index `i` to identify which edition a plugin override applies to. If `msg.editions` is not guaranteed to arrive in a deterministic, stable order (e.g. it is backed by a hash-keyed container in the daemon), the index can drift across calls, silently applying the wrong plugin override. Consider keying by edition ID instead (e.g. `bodyOverwrite_\u003ceditionId\u003e`).",
