      "message": "Line 526: `item.second.commit.value(\"body\")` returns an empty `QString` for interactions whose commit map has no `\"body\"` key (e.g. file-transfer, call records). The QML edit flow calls this role only for messages being edited, but returning an empty pre-filled editor for non-text interactions is confusing. Guard with a type check or document the invariant.",
